<li id="cite_note-woodhead-0"><b><a href="#cite_ref-woodhead_0-0" title="">^</a></b> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="web" id="CITEREFWoodhead2009">Woodhead, Linda (2004). <a href="http://books.google.com/books?id=EsctaP__5yQC&amp;pg=PA34&amp;dq=ignatious+where+the+bishop+is+there+is+the+catholic+church&amp;lr=" class="external text" title="http://books.google.com/books?id=EsctaP__5yQC&amp;pg=PA34&amp;dq=ignatious+where+the+bishop+is+there+is+the+catholic+church&amp;lr=" rel="nofollow">"An Introduction to Christianity"</a>. Cambridge University Press<span class="printonly">. <a href="http://books.google.com/books?id=EsctaP__5yQC&amp;pg=PA34&amp;dq=ignatious+where+the+bishop+is+there+is+the+catholic+church&amp;lr=" class="external free" title="http://books.google.com/books?id=EsctaP__5yQC&amp;pg=PA34&amp;dq=ignatious+where+the+bishop+is+there+is+the+catholic+church&amp;lr=" rel="nofollow">http://books.google.com/books?id=EsctaP__5yQC&amp;pg=PA34&amp;dq=ignatious+where+the+bishop+is+there+is+the+catholic+church&amp;lr=</a></span><span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved on 18 Nov 2008</span>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=bookitem&amp;rft.btitle=An+Introduction+to+Christianity&amp;rft.atitle=&amp;rft.aulast=Woodhead&amp;rft.aufirst=Linda&amp;rft.au=Woodhead%2C+Linda&amp;rft.date=2004&amp;rft.pub=Cambridge+University+Press&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fbooks.google.com%2Fbooks%3Fid%3DEsctaP__5yQC%26pg%3DPA34%26dq%3Dignatious%2Bwhere%2Bthe%2Bbishop%2Bis%2Bthere%2Bis%2Bthe%2Bcatholic%2Bchurch%26lr%3D&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Roman_Catholic_Church"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
