<li id="cite_note-27"><b><a href="#cite_ref-27" title="">^</a></b> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="web" id="CITEREFParagraph_number_8651994">Paragraph number 865 (1994). <a href="http://www.vatican.va/archive/catechism/p123a9p3.htm#IV" class="external text" title="http://www.vatican.va/archive/catechism/p123a9p3.htm#IV" rel="nofollow">"Catechism of the Catholic Church"</a>. Libreria Editrice Vaticana<span class="printonly">. <a href="http://www.vatican.va/archive/catechism/p123a9p3.htm#IV" class="external free" title="http://www.vatican.va/archive/catechism/p123a9p3.htm#IV" rel="nofollow">http://www.vatican.va/archive/catechism/p123a9p3.htm#IV</a></span><span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved on 8 February 2008</span>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=bookitem&amp;rft.btitle=Catechism+of+the+Catholic+Church&amp;rft.atitle=&amp;rft.aulast=Paragraph+number+865&amp;rft.au=Paragraph+number+865&amp;rft.date=1994&amp;rft.pub=Libreria+Editrice+Vaticana&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.vatican.va%2Farchive%2Fcatechism%2Fp123a9p3.htm%23IV&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Roman_Catholic_Church"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
