ki/Roman_Rite" title="Roman Rite">Roman Rite</a> <span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Sarum_Rite" title="Sarum Rite">Sarum Rite</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/East_Syrian_Rite" title="East Syrian Rite">East Syrian Rite</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/West_Syrian_Rite" title="West Syrian Rite">West Syrian Rite</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Anglican_Use" title="Anglican Use">Anglican Use</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Asperges" title="Asperges">Asperges</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Exorcism#Roman_Catholicism" title="Exorcism">Exorcism</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Catholic_Funeral" title="Catholic Funeral">Funeral</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Requiem" title="Requiem">Requiem</a></div>
